        <briefdescription>
<para>Correlate one frame and optionally dump the accumulator. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Steps:<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>FFT(in) → work_fft</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>work_fft[k] *= ref_spec[k]</computeroutput> (frequency-domain multiplication)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>IFFT(work_fft) → work_ifft (unnormalized; divide by n)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>accum[k] += work_ifft[k] / n</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>count++</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>If count == dwell: copy accum → out, zero accum, reset count, return n.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Otherwise: return 0 (no output this call).</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>state</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Must be non-NULL. </para>
</parameterdescription>
